<br>
<br>
Example:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=343063">Level 51 warrior</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
AC 1018<br>
HP  2,395<br>
<br>
Now compare with the mask I want to get:<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=484945">With Stone Visor Instead</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
AC 1042<br>
HP 2,382<br>
<br>
